						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up at the entrance into the Jumma Masjid.</p>						

						<p>Vijayanagara: Pratapadēva.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1351, Pramādhi, Māgha śu. 15</hi> corresponding to 1434 A.D., January 23.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Mentions only the date portion and seems to be a gift of land.</p>						

